908:### 2. NAPI bridge is ~800-1200 lines, not 200
909:The bridge needs to expose `ActorContext` and all sub-objects (`Kv`, `SqliteDb`, `Schedule`, `Queue`, `ConnHandle`, `WebSocket`) as NAPI classes with method bindings. Each callback type needs a `ThreadsafeFunction` wrapper. The existing NAPI layer (`bridge_actor.rs` + `envoy_handle.rs` + `database.rs` ~1430 lines) is a complete rewrite, not an incremental addition.
